<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<title>Unusual Login Attempt</title>
		<style>
			body {
				font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
				background-color: #f5f5f5;
			}
			.container {
				margin: 0 auto;
				max-width: 600px;
				padding: 20px;
				background-color: #fff;
				border-radius: 10px;
				box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
			}
			h1 {
				color: #ca3636;
				font-size: 24px;
				margin: 0 0 20px;
				text-align: center;
			}
			p {
				font-size: 16px;
				line-height: 1.5;
				margin: 0 0 10px;
			}
			.btn {
				display: inline-block;
				padding: 10px 20px;
				border-radius: 5px;
				background-color: #ca3636;
				color: #fff;
				text-decoration: none;
			}
			.btn:hover {
				background-color: #a02d2d;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="container">
			<h1>Unusual Login Attempt</h1>
			<p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
			<p>
				We have detected an unusual login attempt on your account from <%=
				location %> at <%= time %>.
			</p>
			<p>
				If you did not attempt to log in from this location, please click the
				button below to reset your password immediately:
			</p>
			<p>
				<a class="btn" href="">Reset Password</a>
			</p>
			<p>If you have any questions or concerns, please reply to this email.</p>
			<p>Thank you for using our service.</p>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
